    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Your Kids Are Their Problem</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Cecilia Capuzzi Simon letter on Lisa Belkin's July 23 article on backlash against children calls Jason Gill a grump who needs t lighten up4</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Jason Gill made me laugh. He brought back fond memories of the days when two girlfriends and I tormented the kid-hating neighbor whose backyard abutted the yard of my friend's home.</p>
        <p>Gill is a child magnet. He'll never find a peaceful neighborhood in which to reside. He should rediscover the child within and lighten up! He has some legitimate workplace and tax-code gripes, but geez, what a grump.</p>
        <p>Cecilia Capuzzi Simon  Bethesda, Md.</p>
      </block>
